metadata.Plot: Documentary covering the famous 'demonic possession' case of Anneliese Michel. The film features authentic footage of 'exorcisms' and other shocking events, considered to be the inspiration of the film The Exorcism of Emily Rose (2005).
metadata.Actors: Yaz Canli, Kai Cofer, Christopher Karl Johnson, Nikki Muller
